Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.26,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When we started living in \Nthe same dorm together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:21.08,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured trouble would come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.20,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We started talking to each other \Nabout cats he had taken in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.66,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and we even ended up in the \Nsame class in our second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:35.55,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Composing Message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:35.55,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To: {\b0}Former Freeloader
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:39.87,Saku-thought,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall, a congregation of the \Nschool's problem students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:48.57,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,But being in such close proximity...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.31,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,makes some things even harder to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.87,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Expressing these feelings out loud \Nhas gotten a lot more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:36.43,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Could you leave the dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.10,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,just for the night on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.10,Saku-thought,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.62,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:41.99,Saku-thought,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd see what he could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:46.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:47.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mashiron?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:54.21,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}#14 The Windows and Lights of Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:48.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:52.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her publisher's throwing a party on the 24th...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, that just leaves Chihiro-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You two are going on a date, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It might just work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.26,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Please Knock\NMashiron's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.16,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Get out from inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I haven't \Nreally talked to Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.70,Sign,PACKAGE,0000,0000,0000,,Baumkuchen: For Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this little skit all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a skit. I'm eating baumkuchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize if you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what about your manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a lot to do \Nbefore the end of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you, I'm not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.51,Sign,SLIPPERS,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.68,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did I seem to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be satisfied if I tell\N you that you're a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.99,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,That's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.75,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to confess your \Nfeelings to him on the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why do I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:46.92,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun and Shiina-san's relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is on the rocks, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.65,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,And you've got a date with \NKanda-kun on Christmas Eve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses. It's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun is taking Mashiro to a party...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.37,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's picking her up afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:03.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,While he's waiting for her, we're just \Ngoing to watch a play and get dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.68,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,So, basically, a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's {\i1}not{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.64,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.84,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,See? What are you going to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really decided yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.27,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to wear a skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.12,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get careless and wear \Ndenim or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:19.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A skirt, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.49,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Rumi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.49,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to delete this entry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.54,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you study too hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get accepted into \Nan art school in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something you \Nshould say to a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who's working hard to get into \Nthe school of his choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.23,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.49,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I meant, my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you need something, \NStudent Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.25,Saku-main,SOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's "former" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.68,Saku-main,SOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about going to Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.57,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You heard from Hau-hau? \NYou two are rather close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.81,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.27,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you can cope with the distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.69,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,For you, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.80,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll have no trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,finding girls to mess around with \Nas soon as you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.90,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kamiigusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.56,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I already broke up with \Nall the women...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been messing around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:17.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Misaki isn't alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.38,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She has Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.40,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.86,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.73,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.97,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.60,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.23,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She's already looking right at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.26,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:42.86,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't just want her to love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to {\i1}make{\i0} her love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.91,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Because I really do love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.00,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.11,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It makes {\i1}me{\i0} want to marry you, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow this, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Battle underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun will love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you mention Kanda-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting him see my underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:19.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but... Kamiigusa-senpai, \Nare you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:19.87,Saku-main,MASAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:20.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What do I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your confession on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:27.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you afraid to \Ntell him how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Nanamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've liked Jin \Nsince elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I didn't realize how \NI felt until middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But if I think about that \Neven a little, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Fear takes hold and propels\N me around the circle again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.75,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I start by thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:57.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I need to tell Jin how I feel! I can't \Nlive like this anymore!" You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,"But I'm scared. What if he rejects me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, I guess it's not so \Nbad the way things are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be with Jin..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,"But I want to be closer to Jin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,"Jin's dating other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do\N if he goes away?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Which brings me right back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've probably gone through it a \Nhundred times since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:28.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I'm starting to get sick of \Nwatching the same scenery go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to close my eyes and leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:34.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Space, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, you're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not what I meant. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:48.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.37,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.37,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Results of the Screening Process
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.54,Sign,PACKAGE,0000,0000,0000,,Baumkuchen: For Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:09.55,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she had something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.44,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I don't understand \Nhow you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.52,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who's working \Nhard would get angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:20.31,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when they see someone else slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain lines you \Nshouldn't cross with your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.23,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want me to go there \Nbecause you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.19,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You know Mashiro isn't slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:36.15,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn't know how to face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,an emotion she's never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.03,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro doesn't know how \Nto reconcile with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:45.25,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What good will facing her with \Nyour own half-baked feelings do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:47.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to apologize to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.49,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. You're such a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.68,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because if something isn't white, \Nyou reckon it must be black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:57.69,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The world isn't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.91,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Most things aren't that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.43,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They're neither white nor \Nblack. They're gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.80,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.52,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.08,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is, if you become...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:15.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,someone who can only accept \Nhis own ideal scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll make yourself and \Neveryone around you unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that supposed to—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.18,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.13,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm on Mashiro Duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.82,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.63,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm locking up Sakura Hall \Nat the end of this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:33.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.73,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go have \Nsome fun in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.50,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.35,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the day approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.15,Sign,PACKAGE,0000,0000,0000,,Baumkuchen: For Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.73,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings I don't know how to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.74,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings I don't know if I should convey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.79,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings I've decided not to convey yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:08.06,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,They intersect, overlap, collide,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.31,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and pass by each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.69,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,Handmade Cakes Tirol
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you bring a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She said to come by after 5pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sight for sore eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look, kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.78,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cute, you're at a loss for words?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're pretty \Ncomfortable wearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:56.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've worn dresses to award ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here, wear a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you, Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the Sakura Hall party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be exchanging gifts, so don't \Nforget to bring something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.74,Saku-thought,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro doesn't know how \Nto reconcile with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:38.08,Saku-thought,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What good will facing her with \Nyour own half-baked feelings do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the results of the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.65,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.69,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the princess from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back by 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:03.96,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.03,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:06.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:12.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:19.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.65,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing... I'll leave her to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, don't forget to \Ngreet people properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.11,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to act so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I just didn't expect this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant. \NYou just look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Different how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think this side of you isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was pretty taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:30.84,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stupid couples, \Ngo blow yourselves up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.97,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:37.01,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to Ryunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.44,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.77,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,For a country bumpkin like \Nyou to try to set a flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,by sending something like \Nthis is inconceivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.22,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me talk to Ryunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.92,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.32,Sign,WINDOW,0000,0000,0000,,Sora
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if any will stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay if snow falls on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:14.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm letting you use my umbrella, \Nso the least you can do is hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you think of the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It was interesting, but the \Nactors also surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and made me frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:38.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I feel the same \Nway when I play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Professionals are on a \Ncompletely different level than us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from their oratory skills \Nto their acting talents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But, I guess that isn't \Nsomething I should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.91,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to someone who's already \Nworking really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:53.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Still not confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:11.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's an audition for \Nan agency in February.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My parents told me to \Ncome back to Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:19.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if an agency doesn't hire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail the audition, I'll transfer \Nschools and go back to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I pass, I'll work for an agency \Nwhile attending Suimei High.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:31.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be sad if I left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I pass my audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you then, not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once I say it, things will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I promise I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.62,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:22.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-If... If the time comes \Nand I'm hesitating,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,To leap into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what it means? Just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I understand, but sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:38.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.56,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.14,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ayano. Is Shiina-san with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.12,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Shiina-san \Nhas disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:49.84,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel staff said they \Nsaw her go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.19,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea \Nwhere she might have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.12,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:14.87,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.52,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:27.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The snow stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared somewhere \Nwhile I was walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:53.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's good. I wanted you to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:04.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You've been angry a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot I want \Nto talk to you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you always look so unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:15.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it, so I tried to \Nthink of what I could do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:21.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How could I make you happy? \NHow could I make you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:26.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll worry about you if you disappear \Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They said you suddenly vanished \Nand they couldn't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might have been \Ninvolved in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my heart was going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You need more self-awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Walking around here barefoot, \Ncutting your finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're a professional manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I think about you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:22.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It made me want to make lunch for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think of you like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.68,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt this way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you draw manga \Ngave me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You put all you had into drawing, \Nnever thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,compromising or consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You put everything on \Nthe line so naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I haven't been \Nable to take my eyes off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've liked that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have my eyes on you. \NI'm watching you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:04.81,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you two going \Nto stand there like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:18.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew, it'd make you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.74,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game!" Screening Committee Member
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:31.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me prepare \Nfor my presentation again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:18.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:21.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do? \NIt's pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:25.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're getting it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:28.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:31.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:33.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:36.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:44.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I tried really hard \Nso we could be lovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:46.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:50.72,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't treat you right \Nthe way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:52.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fine at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:01.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.95,0:23:02.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:05.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.32,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Stay the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Be the girl I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:16.79,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:20.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin was so nice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:23.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:29.42,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Jin to hurt me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.57,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,He's bringing three girls home with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,#15 Where is My Usual Self?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:40.06,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,It takes only the slightest stimulus \Nfor sons to grow up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,DAD,0000,0000,0000,,So very true...
